## Business Model

### Phase 1 Revenue Engine (Launch)
- **Mobile IV pop-ups** at partner locations (pilates, sauna, gyms, wellness studios)
- **On-call/mobile bookings** — nurse comes to client's home, office, hotel
- **Monthly membership** at $299/month (1 IV + priority booking + discounted add-ons)
- Target: $10K/month MRR by month 4–5

### Phase 1 Service Menu (3 IVs only)
- Hydration Reset
- Immune Support
- Performance / Recovery
- Add-ons: B12, Glutathione

### Phase 2 (Month 5–9)
- GLP-1 weight management programs (recurring subscription)
- NAD+ programs
- Referral program live

### Phase 3 (Month 10+)
- Hormone therapy / perimenopause / HRT (Coco's NP scope enables this)
- Brick + mortar only after $15K/month MRR proven for 3+ months
- Nevada (Incline Village) expansion evaluated after CA stable at 25+ members
- Aesthetic services (PRP, microneedling, injectables) added at Phase 3+

### Pricing
- Average IV ticket: $300 (Bay Area with add-ons)
- Membership: $299/month
- GLP-1 (Phase 2): ~$399/month subscription
- Gross margin per IV: ~73% (cost $50–75 to deliver)
- Member LTV: $3,600 ($299 x 12 months)
- Estimated CAC: $50 (partner referrals + warm network)

